      "content": "i dont even know why im still doing this. the lab results came back and it's just... nothing. another year of work down the drain and the funding is pulling out next month. i feel like there's nothing left of me outside of this degree. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting for something that clearly doesn't want me. i just want it all to stop.",
