      "content": "it feels like more than just a career thing though. like, even if i just quit the lab, the weight of everything else—the expectations, the failure, the feeling that i've wasted my life—it doesn't just go away. it’s constant. i feel like i'm just stuck in this loop of suffering. is there really any way to truly just... stop the noise?",
